message: On Friday, the unveiling of the new website marked a monumental day for the victims of human trafficking in the state of South Carolina. It’s a central place for them to connect with law enforcement officers, attorneys, social services, or simply learn about the laws that are in place to protect them.

data.description: South Carolina is preventing and prosecuting human trafficking crimes, while protecting victims.
data.title: Human Trafficking Task Force unveils new website to connect victims and anti-trafficking advocates in South Carolina
